short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export YouTube transcripts to your clipboard and AI tools like ChatGPT

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transcripti boosts your productivity when working with YouTube videos.

It can copy YouTube transcripts to your clipboard, with or without timestamps. 

It can also send transcripts to tools like ChatGPT in a single click, able to handle longer videos via a multi-part prompt.
Once the transcript is submitted, you can ask questions such as "what are the top 5 points made in this video transcript?"
